    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/7">Otto</persName> superna favente clementia Romanorum <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Omnium fidelium nostrorum
                        tam presentium quam et futurorum noverit universitas, quod nos pro Dei
                        omnipotentis amore animêque nostre remedio ac petitione domni <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1567">Willelmi</persName>, Deo amabilis <rs
                            key="#Abbots">heremite</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Wine #Hay/fodder #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sanctae Mariê quod dicitur in <placeName
                                ref="#places/1558 #places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>,
                        nostra imperiali auctoritate confirmamus omnia quê illo pertinent in
                        quocumque loco maneant, in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscariis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs> et
                        cêteris pertinentiis. Statuimus itaque et precipimus firmiter, concedentes
                        ut nemo ibidem ponatur in abbatem, nisi quem heremitê ibidem Deo militantes
                        eligant communi consilio fratrum. Igitur si quis hoc praeceptum fregerit,
                        componat <rs key="#Penalty">centum libras auri cocti</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camere nostrê</rs> ac <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem predictis fratribus
                            heremitis</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur, hanc paginam manu propria
                        roborantes sigillare precepimus. Signum domni Ottonis caesaris invicti.
                            <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/3962">Heribertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/223">Petri</persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/227"><placeName ref="#places/356"
                                >Cumani</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> recognovit. Data II kal. aprilis, anno
                        dominice incarnationis M primo, indictione XIIII, anno tercii Ottonis
                        regnantis XVII, imperii V. Actum <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >Ravennê</placeName>; feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
